---
title: Summer Halloumi Salad with Strawberry Dressing and Orange Segments
description: Get ready to feel the sunshine! Tonight's dinner is a pop of bright summery flavours with a strawberry vinaigrette that clings to sweet snap peas, juicy oranges, and salty crisp halloumi. It's a boost of instant Vitamin C!
